276.japanese: 半田さん　もっと教えてあげて 僕のかわいいとこ
276.english: Tell them even more cute things about me, Mr. Handa.

277.speaker: HANDA
277.japanese: 竹しか食べてないから
277.english: Since they only eat bamboo, pandas' poop smells good.

278.speaker: HANDA
278.japanese: ちょっと レモンのにおいに似ているんです

279.speaker: HANDA
279.japanese: あぁ…　これ　これ

280.speaker: HANDA
280.japanese: うん　パンダのウンチのにおいです
280.english: Yes, it smells like panda poop. Here, try it.

281.speaker: KIRINO
281.japanese: 先輩！　その情報は いらないんじゃないですか？
281.english: Mr. Handa! I don't think they need that information.

282.speaker: PANDA
282.japanese: もう！　もっと かわいいエピソードにしてよ
282.english: Come on, tell them something cuter than that.

283.speaker: HANDA
283.english: Oh, really? Pandas look cute with their droopy eyes, right?

284.speaker: HANDA
284.japanese: あれって　実際の目は 小さくて　鋭いんですよ
284.english: In actuality, their actual eye is small and very sharp. They don't need to know that either.

285.speaker: HANDA
285.english: Really? I think that's really cute.

287.speaker: SASAKO
287.japanese: ペンギンさん　カフェモカ　おかわり お待たせしました
287.english: Mr. Penguin, here you go, your refill on the café mocha.

289.speaker: GIRL
289.japanese: 今度　パンダコーナー 遊びにいってもいいですか？
289.english: Is it okay if we come by the panda corner sometime?

290.speaker: HANDA
290.japanese: もちろんです　見にきてください
290.english: Of course. Please come. I'll introduce you to Mr. Full-time Panda, too.

291.speaker: GIRL
291.japanese: 常勤パンダさん？ このパンダさんは何なんですか？
291.english: Mr. Full-time Panda? So what's this panda, then?

292.speaker: HANDA
292.english: He's a part-time panda that works two days a week.

293.speaker: GIRL
293.japanese: へぇ～　アルバイトなんだ？

300.speaker: PENGUIN
300.japanese: どうも　こんばんは

302.speaker: PANDA
302.japanese: 忙しいんじゃなかったの？ ペンギンさん

306.speaker: PENGUIN
306.english: Ma-Ma-halo! Yay! Yay! Yay! Yay! Mr. Penguin, could I have the mic now?

307.speaker: PENGUIN
307.english: I'm singing one more song! One more song!

310.speaker: KIRINO
310.english: He's asleep! Wake up, Panda. Wake up!

313.speaker: GIRL
313.japanese: ねぇ　なんか似てない？

314.speaker: PENGUIN
314.japanese: このカフェにたどり着いた ラッキーボーイズ　アンド　ガールズ
314.english: You lucky boys and girls who found this café

315.speaker: GIRL
315.japanese: 今日は　ありがとうございました
315.english: Thank you very much for today.

316.speaker: GIRL
316.english: It was a lot of fun!

317.speaker: GIRL
317.japanese: また　パンダの話聞かせてください
317.english: Tell us more about pandas next time! Sure. Please visit the zoo.

318.speaker: GIRLS
318.japanese: はい じゃあ　おやすみなさい

319.speaker: HANDA
319.japanese: それじゃ　俺も 風呂の掃除あるから　帰るわ
319.english: Okay, I have to go clean my bathroom, so I'm heading off.

323.speaker: POLAR BEAR
323.japanese: うちで　コーヒーでも飲んでく？
323.english: Did you want to have some coffee at my place?

324.speaker: KIRINO
324.japanese: はい　シロクマさん

327.speaker: PENGUIN
327.japanese: あっ！　あれ？　みんなは？
